<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
    <section class="rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-800 via-emerald-700 to-lime-600 p-8 text-white shadow-[0_28px_90px_rgba(21,128,61,0.24)] lg:p-10">
        <p class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-white/15 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-50">New Member Onboarding</p>
        <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight">Gabung ke sistem komunitas yang mencatat aksi lingkungan secara nyata.</h1>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-7 text-emerald-50/90">
            Buat akun untuk mulai mengirim log sampah, mendapatkan poin setelah verifikasi, dan ikut dalam ekosistem warga yang lebih terukur.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-white/10 p-5 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <p class="font-bold text-white">Data lingkungan lebih tertata</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-emerald-50/90">Setiap akun terhubung dengan RT/RW agar kontribusi warga bisa dipetakan dengan rapi.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-white/10 p-5 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <p class="font-bold text-white">Poin berbasis verifikasi</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-emerald-50/90">Kontribusi tidak sekadar dihitung otomatis, tetapi divalidasi agar hasilnya kredibel.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/95 p-8 shadow-[0_18px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] backdrop-blur lg:p-10">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-100 pb-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-600">Create Account</p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Join the Eco-Pulse community</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">Lengkapi data berikut untuk membuat akun warga atau admin komunitas.</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/register" method="POST" class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Username</label>
                <input type="text" name="username" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" placeholder="ecowarrior" required>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">RT</label>
                <input type="text" name="rt" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" placeholder="05" required>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">RW</label>
                <input type="text" name="rw" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" placeholder="02" required>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Join As</label>
                <select name="role" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100">
                    <option value="citizen">Citizen (Warga)</option>
                    <option value="admin">Admin (Pengurus)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Password</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-800 transition focus:border-emerald-500 focus:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" placeholder="Minimum 8 characters" required>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-5 py-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                Pastikan RT/RW sesuai area Anda. Informasi ini dipakai untuk pelacakan kontribusi komunitas dan leaderboard lingkungan.
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Sudah punya akun? <a href="/login" class="font-bold text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800">Login di sini</a>.</p>
                <button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-700 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-[0_12px_30px_rgba(21,128,61,0.24)] transition hover:bg-emerald-800">Create Account</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </section>
</div>
